<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Metro buys Bloch marks business.</title>
<headline>Metro buys Bloch marks business.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-05-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bloch Ltd said on Wednesday it had sold its trade marks and business operations as a going concern to Metro Cash and Carry Ltd.</p>
<p>The cash purchase consideration is 19.64 million rand and the effective date of the deal is April 30, 1997.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
